PathologicalPathFilter does filter out repetitions like 
/bla/?id=27/bla/?id=27/bla/?id=27/.

The regex it uses is this (with the default maxRepetions=2): 
.*?/(.*?/)&#92;1{2,}.*
You can test it with this tool among others: 
http://www.fileformat.info/tool/regex.htm

Noah


